divs: Sighting DetailsMy friend and i were chaging the front brakes on his mustang.when i noticed the object the weird thing is i just felt like i should look up in that direction.Like it was watching us or something.The object was pulsing chainging shape.It is hard to explain it was just white like a illuminated object. But i could deffinatly tell it was pulsing or morphing i cant explain it.The oject was very close at first but as we began to point and look at it it slowly moved up and went towards naples. It moved very slow. It seemed to leave some kind of trail very faint. If someone were to look up and see it they would probaly say it is just a balloon or something. But my friend and i seen it changing shape.I have also seen many other ufos over kings peak if anyone else has see or heard of things over kings peak or the Baldys please let me know. People think i am just weird or sometning. But iknow what i have seen. I have heard rumors about kings peak area if anone else knows more let me know. dbartlett@rconnects.com
Summary: Seen hovering over trees hard to make out a certain shape.
